                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p><iframe src="/greenwolf-s-author-page/html/9a9e6b1ffeb7c151c54ae35914ac679dbaba51e6-4400072021094239955" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">rating:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+41</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="I like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="I don't like it" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="Cancel my vote" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<div style="border: solid 5px #999999; background:#eef0f2; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><strong>Name:</strong> M.T. Bade<br />
<strong>Twitter:</strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/MTBade">@MTBade</a><br />
<strong>Website:</strong> <a href="http://mtbade.com">mtbade.com</a><br />
<strong>Ko-fi:</strong> <a href="https://ko-fi.com/mtbade">ko-fi.com/mtbade</a></p>
<p><strong>About:</strong> Hi, I'm Matt, and I write stories when I'm not procrastinating on writing stories. In real life, I'm an undergrad physicist working to escape from Hell (aka Arizona). In addition to writing for this site, I also write original short fiction for professional publication, and occasionally blog about the idiosyncrasies of the Grand Canyon State.</p>
<p><strong>Who Gets My Stuff If I Vanish:</strong> <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span> and/or <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span></p>
</div>
